---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import BackgroundNotebook from "../assets/quote/bg.png";
import Quote from "../assets/quote/quote.png";
import Guide from "../assets/testimony-guide.svg";
---

<section class="relative isolate mt-24">
  <Image
    class="absolute left-0 right-0 -z-10 mx-auto h-full object-cover"
    alt=""
    src={BackgroundNotebook}
  />

  <div
    class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-5xl flex-col items-center font-display font-medium text-[#141392] lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_auto_1fr] lg:items-start"
  >
    <div
      class="mt-20 flex aspect-square h-24 items-center justify-center justify-self-start rounded-full bg-[hsl(0,0%,95%)] lg:ml-auto"
    >
      <Image alt="" class="aspect-[68/45] w-3/5" src={Quote} />
    </div>

    <p
      class="mx-auto mt-20 max-w-[41ch] px-6 text-center text-2xl font-medium lg:mt-20 lg:text-4xl"
    >
      By leaving my inheritance to Mama Cash, I feel like I am sustaining our
      family heritage, not through offspring, but by contributing to a better
      world for women and girls. I have no doubt that my inheritance will
      contribute to change for women and girls. I trust Mama Cash completely,
      she puts her money where her mouth is.
    </p>

    <h3
      class="col-start-2 mx-auto mt-9 text-center text-2xl font-semibold text-[#E91E78] lg:text-3xl"
    >
      Sandrine Ulemberg
    </h3>
    <p class="col-start-2 mx-auto mb-20 text-center font-medium uppercase">
      Mama Cash individual donor
    </p>

    <div
      class="relative col-start-3 row-span-2 row-start-2 hidden aspect-square h-24 items-center justify-center justify-self-end rounded-full bg-[hsl(0,0%,95%)] lg:flex"
    >
      <Image
        class="invisible absolute left-7 -z-10 h-[1687px] max-w-[867px] lg:visible"
        alt=""
        src={Guide}
      />
      <Image class="aspect-[68/45] w-3/5 -scale-100" alt="" src={Quote} />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
